```
import presentor from 'presentor'

var model = {

  width: 500,
  height: 500,

  components: [{
    id: 1,
    type: 'rect',

    left: 100,
    top: 100,
    width: 200,
    height: 200
  }, {
    id: 2,
    type: 'rect',

    left: 500,
    top: 100,
    width: 200,
    height: 200
  }],

  links: [{
    from: 1,
    to: 2
  }]
};

var target = 'presenter';

var p1 = presentor.create({ target, model });
```
